          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Free browser version — no signup, no friction</h4><p>Open the URL, paste your text, see the results. The lowest barrier to entry on this list.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: no saving in browser version and no SEO features</h4><p>Clarity only — not grammar, not SEO, not publishing. Use it as a final readability pass before moving to Yoast or Surfer.</p></div></li>
