          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Are free blog writing tools good enough?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Starting out, yes. Google Docs + Grammarly + WordPress + Yoast provides a fully functional free stack. The limitation is time — you're still researching, writing, optimizing, and publishing manually. When you want to scale past 4 posts per month, paid automation tools become necessary.</div>
