          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do I need an AI writing tool for blogging?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Not required, but the economics are hard to ignore. Manual 2,000-word posts take 4 hours; AI assistance cuts that to 30–60 minutes. theStacc eliminates the time cost entirely — 30 posts per month for $99 with no writing hours.</div>
