          <div class="faq-answer">Blog writing tools create content. SEO tools help that content rank. Some tools combine both — theStacc handles keyword research, writing, and SEO optimization as a single automated pipeline, so the distinction doesn't apply.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can blog writing tools replace freelance writers?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">For most informational SEO content, yes. AI tools produce content at $3–$9 per article versus $80–$250 from freelancers. The quality gap has narrowed significantly for general-topic SEO content. Highly specialized or regulated topics still benefit from human expertise.</div>
